{"tid":2273164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰反政府領袖：改革王室寸步不讓","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T13:56:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b434d7531854a0bb09e973c4a87ba1fe3426cd76","tid":2273164,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201105/RB7K4EBGDBF5XB5EQTEG22GS4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201105%2FRB7K4EBGDBF5XB5EQTEG22GS4E%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=cf2f7f79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201105%2FRB7K4EBGDBF5XB5EQTEG22GS4E%2F&h=e67f3935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201105/RB7K4EBGDBF5XB5EQTEG22GS4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n泰反政府領袖：改革王室寸步不讓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B9a7z9U72hRGW9CPStqbgmj5MDc=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PSPLFDAYZRAMLGQUDXKUVLO6ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB9a7z9U72hRGW9CPStqbgmj5MDc%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPSPLFDAYZRAMLGQUDXKUVLO6ZE.jpg&h=cd25671d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■泰國人權律師阿農（右二）與三名示威戰友前日步出監獄時，一同舉起三指抗爭手勢。<br />\n<br />\n泰國反政府示威領袖、人權律師阿農前日表明，不會在改革王室這項訴求上讓步，又指如月中的國會會議不通過示威者要求的修憲，將會在國會外發起示威。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n復會後修憲不果將示威<br />\n<br />\n警方向法庭要求延長關押阿農與另外三名示威者領袖被拒，他們前日在曼谷一個監獄獲釋。警方就多場示威集會向他們提出多項起訴，包括非法使用大聲公煽動公眾。<br />\n<br />\n阿農向在場過百名支持者說：「當國會復會後沒有通過修憲，我們會親手關閉國會。」。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「暴力不是答案。我們的對手也會知道。和平、真誠和人性是我們的原則」。<br />\n<br />\n示威者認為王室擁有太多權力；王室支持者就認為憲法是國家的靈魂，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"58e412dfe0622aff075aff84ac22f71ed24a6263","tid":2273164,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"支持 死幾多人都唔可以讓 要俾政權知道決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人就係輸呢樣"},{"pid":"f4441394da6ec0239521c7c2a2b3a76666ac1ac9","tid":2273164,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"今時今日民主都敵唔過人民幣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}